Two people have been reportedly dead and several injured in a Train-Bus accident on old Abeokuta road, Agege, Lagos. It was gathered that the victims were sitting on the train when it veered upon sighting the bus from afar. According to eye-witnesses the victims fell on the rail-line and was shredded by the moving train, while the other two fell by the bus, losing some body parts. Emergency agencies, however, have arrived on the scene for recovery and evacuation. Details soonâ€¦ To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .